Convert a numeric variable for hours into categorical

Source: R/cut_hour.R
cut_hour.Rd

Supply a numeric variable, e.g. Collaboration_hours, and the function returns a character vector

cut_hour(metric, cuts, unit = "hours")

Arguments

metric

A numeric variable representing hours.
cuts

A numeric variable of minimum length 3 to represent the cut points required.
unit

String to specify the unit of the labels. Defaults to "hours".
